EnExplanation: A term used to refer to an item, object, or matter of some significance or importance.

Samples.EeSentence: Mul on üks asi, mille ma pean tegema.
Samples.EnSentence: I have one thing that I need to do.

Samples.EeSentence: Mul on üks oluline asi teha.
Samples.EnSentence: I have one important thing to do.
